{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Install (manual ZIP)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab In REAPER: {\b Options \u8594 ? Show REAPER resource path in explorer/finder\u8230 ?}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Unzip the ZIP {\b into that resource folder} (the folder that already contains {\f1 Scripts/}, {\f1 Effects/}, {\f1 Data/}, {\f1 FXChains/} \u8230 ?).\par}
